{"tid":197201,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"細迴旋處應該邊面行先","createTime":"2017-04-11T18:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T06:35:13.000Z","uid":65793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a9e2418294a9e91df0b1d624c4d3395ec494b2a","tid":197201,"uid":65793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T18:10:59.000Z","msg":"唔知行定讓"},{"pid":"6d20bc4f9f8ef960b5f648466d4a251b890f51ca","tid":197201,"uid":105483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知行定讓</blockquote><br />\n你講地下無劃線既迴旋處？有無地點實例？😂"},{"pid":"adf325e3b9d9513f38a4082f8337357485d62a99","tid":197201,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:33:36.000Z","msg":"你講乜尻？入迴旋？定迴圈內外？"},{"pid":"a11b65328e1d08dc2b1217344b87d1ca824ad848","tid":197201,"uid":65793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0swxcWK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0swxcWK.jpg&h=73eb826e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如這樣，四邊都係讓牌，如果我各在不同路口應該邊面行先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf1d8a8276aba1fd51b3b7261098f48cf408201","tid":197201,"uid":16471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T18:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0swxcWK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0swxcWK.jpg&h=73eb826e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如這樣，四邊都係讓牌，如果我各在不同路口應該邊面行先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無車咪去囉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b2de6802217d8552def1c64d1a91d389ab96be","tid":197201,"uid":65793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T18:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0swxcWK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0swxcWK.jpg&h=73eb826e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如這樣，四邊都係讓牌，如果我各在不同路口應該邊面行先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無車咪去囉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌但係呢個位成日都有車<br />\n<br />\n唔行又砵 行左又一齊出<br />\n<br />\n是咪要讓右邊先"},{"pid":"3b82c82679052d1f1823a41f7b7125b02f5ceb33","tid":197201,"uid":62061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T19:19:42.000Z","msg":"係咪好似青衣Esso對出果個咁"},{"pid":"3d95dce1148eb0d13d1fd99d47d3f201038a4712","tid":197201,"uid":37660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T19:20:30.000Z","msg":"永遠讓右邊"},{"pid":"c26f4c7ff6da346f496460e1294c9557cb632248","tid":197201,"uid":65793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T19:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永遠讓右邊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n周末呢個位經常四邊都有車<br />\n<br />\n邊面可以行先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc73a274843f0095f6309d9a1abcb89e18d59146","tid":197201,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0swxcWK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0swxcWK.jpg&h=73eb826e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如這樣，四邊都係讓牌，如果我各在不同路口應該邊面行先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無車咪去囉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌但係呢個位成日都有車<br />\n<br />\n唔行又砵 行左又一齊出<br />\n<br />\n是咪要讓右邊先</blockquote><br />\n砵都唔好理佢<br />\n撞左嘅話砵你條友冇責任<br />\n仲可以食花生<br />\n一定讓右邊行先<br />\n如果出事嘅話你唔讓正線就輸左七成"},{"pid":"84a143f9d934f3c67d2633d5ff268789b15df7ec","tid":197201,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>永遠讓右邊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n周末呢個位經常四邊都有車<br />\n<br />\n邊面可以行先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果以你幅圖<br />\n你要先讓右面車<br />\n<br />\n如果你入到迴旋處<br />\n左面讓線車要讓你行"},{"pid":"9cd901a11dedc45d1e1f264bdb32bac8bf0b580a","tid":197201,"uid":65793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:48:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>永遠讓右邊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n周末呢個位經常四邊都有車<br />\n<br />\n邊面可以行先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果以你幅圖<br />\n你要先讓右面車<br />\n<br />\n如果你入到迴旋處<br />\n左面讓線車要讓你行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我上面幅圖右邊條線，理應行先<br />\n但右線都有讓牌<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yw40yfq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fyw40yfq.jpg&h=6a00f7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而右線既右線都係讓牌<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UdovNRZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUdovNRZ.jpg&h=aaa68f36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而右線既右線既右線都係讓牌<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ZPB3MkF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZPB3MkF.jpg&h=58c23a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而右線既右線既右線既右線 就係我原先個位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a098cbf50d3c5029163678174f4df0c17c830e","tid":197201,"uid":65793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PAqO47R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPAqO47R.jpg&h=122098c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我都係等右邊踩得慢偷雞攝出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa8cef3614eb76e4109f6d9b8ab0a49b8b26f8f","tid":197201,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:58:04.000Z","msg":"出到唔撞咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手車唔得咪慢慢等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454260c7796e35d9cc185718879b50976a95c482","tid":197201,"uid":61983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:25:58.000Z","msg":"右面係指已經入左迴旋處，由右手面黎既車<br />\n<br />\n係右面讓字牌後面既車，都未入迴旋處，讓黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9775dd94c34aba83f4f5261406912b9b7ae9fe","tid":197201,"uid":22135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"邊個惡就邊個先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你唔出，無人會讓你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">右邊</span></span>"},{"pid":"7646ead16b0fe825ec5a3f35c4d4db4f05c17736","tid":197201,"uid":6778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"停係讓線call拖車幫你拖過去"},{"pid":"ce99b4718607b73fa4f1387e7c8f18b8e6d0b44c","tid":197201,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"自己執生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a7b2b86600a5f10d854f02bf04c4324588332f","tid":197201,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"當幾個路口都有讓牌,其實大家都係玩緊心理戰,根據敵不動,我不動原則,大家都唔好郁,當有一方頂唔順開車嗰刻,你就要睇準時機等架車過咗就行得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f1e2229905e605a8bbe6ee1558e360036ab90c","tid":197201,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T06:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪好似青衣Esso對出果個咁</blockquote><br />\n果個細到整一線算啦 整兩條根本行唔到 同 無人咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4cea97c21db758dd4e0f56364fb6e42677e0b2","tid":197201,"uid":43734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0swxcWK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0swxcWK.jpg&h=73eb826e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如這樣，四邊都係讓牌，如果我各在不同路口應該邊面行先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無車咪去囉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌但係呢個位成日都有車<br />\n<br />\n唔行又砵 行左又一齊出<br />\n<br />\n是咪要讓右邊先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讓右加自己醒水<br />\n<br />\n唔洗人教啦，你讓佢佢唔出你咪嗱嗱聲行囉<br />\n<br />\n入咗迴旋處之後就要小心啲唔撚睇讓牌大撚曬衝出嚟嘅盲毛黑柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1f316d4ff1a6077fd7a065555aa488694cb80c","tid":197201,"uid":76112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:47:16.000Z","msg":"迴旋處好難用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce4a3339723c2a47c1aaff8223ade8b086d795e","tid":197201,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:53:01.000Z","msg":"行路算啦 唔好害人"},{"pid":"c4b45b84f6d98446c27270786dbbc3e9e35c5a91","tid":197201,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:53:45.000Z","msg":"理論上讓右<br />\n不過好多盲毛or仆街唔讓<br />\n所以要自己執生"},{"pid":"f0943adafb19fe5b97b974b98475fa783937d0f9","tid":197201,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"係圈入邊既由十二點方向順時針 有車就唔出 而你下一個入口有車理應佢讓你 佢唔讓你你可以炒埋去拎賠償"}]}